d conv has the shape (in_channels, out_channels, kH, kW) while the weight of vanilla conv has the shape (out_channels, in_channels, kH, kW)\nRuntimeError: Given transposed=1, weight of size [channel1, channel2, kH, kW], expected bias to be 1-dimensional with channel2 elements, but got bias of size [channel1] instead", "merged": false, "mergeable": null, "rebaseable": null, "mergeable_state": "unknown", "merged_by": null, "comments": 3, "review_comments": 0, "maintainer_can_modify": false, "commits": 1, "additions": 36, "deletions": 39, "changed_files": 2}